EXTRACT <%= @process %>

RMTHOST <%= @remote_host %>, mgrport <%= @remote_port %>, ENCRYPT AES128, TIMEOUT 120, PARAMS -UL, COMPRESS

RMTTRAIL ./dirdat/<%= @trail_location %>/tr<%= @trail_format_option %>
PASSTHRU

discardfile ./dirrpt/<%= @process %>.dsc, megabytes 100, append
discardrollover at 00:01

STATOPTIONS RESETREPORTSTATS
Report at 23:55
ReportRollover at 00:01 on sunday

--REPORTCOUNT EVERY 5 MINTUES RATE

